OL,3,CFire chief defends appointment of man
OL,4,Cat centre of bullying allegations
OL,6,Ffire chief Dawn Docx has publicly
OL,7,Fdefended appointing her deputy, Stuart
OL,8,FMillington, despite him being at the
OL,9,Fcentre of bullying allegations.
OL,11,FMr Millington was appointed as interim
OL,12,Ffire chief of the troubled South Wales
OL,13,Fservice on February 12, joining from
OL,14,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,15,Fwhere he was assistant chief fire
OL,16,Fofficer.
