OL,6,FHe was brought in by Welsh Government-
OL,7,Fappointed commissioners to oversee
OL,8,Fchange at the service following a
OL,9,Fdamning independent review in South
OL,10,FWales. The review - prompted by an -
OL,11,Frevealed sexual harassment and
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse were "tolerated" at the
OL,13,Fservice, with a damning report making
OL,14,F82 recommendations to help change its
OL,15,Fculture.
