OL,6,FJust days after Mr Millington's
OL,7,Fappointment, he was himself at the
OL,8,Fcentre of bullying allegations, which
OL,9,Fhe denies, relating to his employment
OL,10,Fin North Wales. He, along with the
OL,11,Fservice, is facing an employment
OL,12,Ftribunal, with a hearing scheduled for
OL,13,FMay.
