OL,3,CFire chief defends appointment of man
OL,4,Cat centre of bullying allegations
OL,6,FAddressing Mr Millington's appointment
OL,7,Fpublicly, Ms Docx was quizzed about
OL,8,Fthe matter on Radio Wales Breakfast on
OL,9,FTuesday - the day after the Welsh
OL,10,FGovernment announced that both North
OL,11,FWales and Mid and West Wales fire and
OL,12,Frescue services will themselves
OL,13,Fundergo an independent review into
OL,14,Ftheir own cultures.
OL,16,F"Can I clarify, the allegations were
OL,17,Fthoroughly investigated," she said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/12
