OL,4,Cat centre of bullying allegations
OL,6,F"We don't have fear or favour, it
OL,7,Fdoesn't matter what level you are in
OL,8,Fthe organisation, we will have an
OL,9,Finvestigation if there is a complaint.
OL,11,F"The findings of that investigation
OL,12,Fmeant that yes, there was some
OL,13,Flearning on both sides and the
OL,14,Forganisation, but it wouldn't have
OL,15,Fbeen anything that would have
OL,16,Fprecluded him taking up that role as
OL,17,Finterim chief fire officer."
OL,19,FPressed on whether she thought it was
OL,20,Fan appropriate appointment, the fire
OL,21,Fchief said: "Yes."
