OL,6,FAs for the wider culture at North
OL,7,FWales Fire and Rescue Service, Ms Docx
OL,8,Fsaid: "I think we're a growing
OL,9,Forganisation, and yes, all fire and
OL,10,Frescue services have had that past
OL,11,Fthat was macho, that was hierarchical,
OL,12,Fbut moving forward we're not in that
OL,13,Fplace anymore and I'm very grateful
OL,14,Fthat the deputy minister listened to
OL,15,Fus and recognises that we genuinely do
OL,16,Fwant to improve and she's given us
OL,17,Fthis opportunity with the independent
OL,18,Freview to not only look at ourselves
OL,19,Fand assess what we're doing but also
OL,20,Flearn what we can do better.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/12
