OL,4,Cat centre of bullying allegations
OL,6,F"Culture doesn't just sort of stop, it
OL,7,Fdoesn't just finish at one point and
OL,8,Fthen flip over and change. It's a
OL,9,Fcontinuum and there are people out
OL,10,Fthere who are still hurting from maybe
OL,11,Finjustices in the past. My message to
OL,12,Fthem would be please, please come
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
