OL,4,Cat centre of bullying allegations
OL,6,F"I know it's awful to suffer in
OL,7,Fsilence and I know it's also difficult
OL,8,Fto have that trust that you'll be
OL,9,Fbelieved and we'll listen and we'll
OL,10,Fact on it, but I want you to come
OL,11,Fforward because we want to help you
OL,12,Fand by helping each individual person
OL,13,Fand hearing their story and acting on
OL,14,Fit, we can then take the organisation
OL,15,Finto the future.
