OL,6,F"If nobody comes forward, if we don't
OL,7,Fhear those complaints, then we can't
OL,8,Fget better. Difficult though it might
OL,9,Fbe for I and my colleagues to hear
OL,10,Fwhat people have experienced, we want
OL,11,Fto know about it and all I can say
OL,12,Fagain is please trust us, come forward
OL,13,Fand let us hear what you're
OL,14,Fexperiencing."
OL,16,FITV Wales requested an interview with
OL,17,FMs Docx but this was declined.
