OL,6,FAppearing before a Senedd committee on
OL,7,FMonday 11 March, Ms Docx said in the
OL,8,Fpast organisations have been "quick"
OL,9,Fto suspend people.
OL,11,FShe said: "We try where we can to keep
OL,12,Fthem in the workplace and connected to
OL,13,Fthe workplace but keep them separate
OL,14,Ffrom the person who has put the
OL,15,Fcomplaint in and any circumstances
OL,16,Fthat might risk having an impact on
OL,17,Fthat investigation."
